metadata.name: Casamigos 1
metadata.description:
Casamigos para Casanakas! 

Casamigos editions are your keys to your future Casanakas, personalized houses for your Nakamigo(s).

Once you minted at least one Casamigos, check my Twitter/pinned tweet to find out how to order your own Casanakas, then DM me your request asap. 

1 edition = 1 request = 1 house. 
Every edition can only be used once for requesting Casanakas. If you want more Casanakas, mint more editions of Casamigos.

For each minted edition, your wallet will be airdropped a house for your Nakamigos in 24-72 hrs from DM!
